Title: New alert handler for safely executing remote commands on Linux hosts
Level: 3
Edition: cee
Component: alerts
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.4.0i1
Date: 1469099469
Class: feature

Check_MK now ships it's own system for safely executing commands on remote
Linux hosts via SSH. Everything is setup with the agent bakery - including SSH
key exchange. Please refer to the new article in the user manual for details.
